====== inet-4.x ======

2017-09-27  Zoltan Bojthe

	Added CRC mode handling.

2017-04-12  Levente Mészáros

	Removed discouraged setChunkLength calls from deserializers.

2017-04-05  Zoltan Bojthe

	Dropped PingPayload, icmp headers contain the identifier and sequence number.

2017-03-01  Levente Mészáros

	Ported IGMPHeaderSerializer to new API.

2017-02-22  Levente Mészáros

	Extracted PingPayloadSerializer.
	Ported serialization of IPv4 options.

2017-02-21  Levente Mészáros

	Ported IPv4HeaderSerializer and ICMPHeaderSerializer to new API.
